      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"let myself fade away\"... that sounds almost peaceful, i guess. but it's also terrifying. because if the person who actually lived is already gone, then what's even left to hold onto? it feels like i'm just waiting for the rest of me to catch up to the part that already died.",
